title: Flextronics on the Importance of Prototyping
text:
Expand Morten Lund, Senior Director of Business Development, EMEA and Marcin Lagoda, NPI QA Engineer, Flextronics International , explain how prototyping remains at the heart of successful production and how this is deployed in a large multinational operation at the TCT Show + Personalize 2015 Conference. 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel . Tags
